About Us

The company DEBROWN has been engaged in landscaping, space design and urban environment for more than 7 years. Combining in our work original ideas of designers, profound knowledge of architects and reliable technologies of practical engineers our team is able to create the most unexpected and diverse projects.

We help to recreate your dreams when decorating your holiday. We can create a cozy corner of nature in the middle of an urban landscape. We carry out large-scale complex projects of urban landscaping on a turnkey basis.

We are guided by the goals and financial capabilities of our clients when we create a project.

We're always willing to go outside the box, but always consider the necessary safety standards when implementing any project.

The company has implemented several hundred successful projects.

Creating constructions and art-objects for New Year decoration, as well as for summer city beautification, we understand that it should:

  • be harmoniously woven into the surrounding space;
  • create a unique, aesthetic atmosphere;
  • form an environment, in which each resident will feel comfortable and safe.

That is why we pay special attention to the peculiarities of the location: its history, architectural surroundings and even climatic conditions.

The high efficiency of our work is based on three important advantages

Creative design team
They are the ones who are brave and enthusiastic about creative ideas and inspire all the company's employees to create unique themed collections, which are presented in our portfolio.
Own production
We work according to the principle of the complete cycle, which allows us to implement the most unexpected ideas. After engineering studies and technical designs, prototypes are created in our own production facilities. After passing the safety and quality tests, the new designs are put into series production. All elements undergo mandatory anti-corrosion treatment. They are reliable and durable.
Individual solution
Each city has its own way of life and unique local flavor. When creating something new, it is very important not to break established traditions, but to play with them competently, emphasizing the best and most valuable. On the other hand, we think that it is necessary to change the existing environment, making it more functional and fascinatingly beautiful at the same time. The task of our team is to find a solution that combines all the elements of this idea and creates a new, unique space that everyone can feel good in. Let's create together!

Order festive decorations and urban environment design for you from 1 day

We will take care of everything from idea to implementation, and we will exceed your expectations by creating a fabulous atmosphere with incredible emotions
